{"tid":1785826,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[追殺] 遭拒入境內地 東區區議員古桂耀：料當局有黑名單","createTime":"2019-12-16T16:26:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-17T03:34:20.000Z","uid":224066,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c1fe4030142fa1f755143bc15fae1f611ed48e38","tid":1785826,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:26:24.000Z","msg":"現任東區區議員古桂耀今日在facebook發文，指自己被內地當局扣查逾一小時後，被告知拒絕入境。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/J3powS5XzGz.AloZcpPqug--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20191216a192158.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FJ3powS5XzGz.AloZcpPqug--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20191216a192158.jpg&h=2f1b688f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n古桂耀中午在網上發文，指原本計劃於今早乘搭直通巴士經深圳灣口岸過關，再轉搭國內巴士到肇慶「還神」。然而，在抵達口岸內地關口的通關閘機時，只能通過手指模驗測，而未能通過人面識別系統。他續指，其後被內地警務人員帶到一間房間等候，而行李及手機亦不能跟身。約30分鐘後，他被一男一女便裝警察帶到另一間房間，女警取去典其身份証後離開，男警則問他為何到內地，古桂耀表明他此行是回內地「還神」，並指男警要求他打開背包及解鎖手機。<br />\n<br />\n古桂耀指，逾一小時後，一名高級警察進入房間後，並指帶他回香港。他隨即反問對方，為何拒絕他入境，並重申自己只是一個人回來「還神」，但對方回答指「不清楚」。他再追問，自己是否永久不可到大陸時，對方則指，「不清楚！今天就是不可以入境！」他又指，整個過程「很禮貌」。他續指，自己並沒有告知內地當局自己為區議員，並指瘁有關部門可查到其身份及知悉他連任。他又認為，內地各個關口已有黑名單，相信會有其他現任或候任區議員未能前往內地。<br />\n<br />\n在今屆區議會選舉中，古桂耀以3,569票擊敗民建聯劉淑燕，並於東區翠灣選區成功連任。"},{"pid":"e8365120aa32fda09ecea6d680c21466707d8949","tid":1785826,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:26:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽晚7點愛丁堡見</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">哀悼香港人道災難</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pie4mpm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPie4mpm.jpg&h=4cc5750a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由於明日主題為哀悼 <br />\n請各位穿黑衫到場以示哀悼<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O1U75uD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO1U75uD.png&h=d951bb19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n面對社署打壓 我地更要齊心"},{"pid":"a336d699c0837387185a29d766591da8b7f6bc81","tid":1785826,"uid":75823,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:29:42.000Z","msg":"放你入支那你仲驚<br />\n放隻雞又你房, 你一枝公即刻仆街"},{"pid":"cb9183a65b35850e7867266561f12b39800c3c8c","tid":1785826,"uid":26333,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:31:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f77a56cacf924d354994dd0e799fb3515923a84","tid":1785826,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a336d699c0837387185a29d766591da8b7f6bc81","tid":1785826,"uid":75823,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:29:42.000Z","msg":"放你入支那你仲驚<br />\n放隻雞又你房, 你一枝公即刻仆街"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:33:14.000Z","msg":"Agger"},{"pid":"5f21d1815dfbf7f57792e8ae7d927d343fa920da","tid":1785826,"uid":334806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:33:56.000Z","msg":"又懲罰班中國豬民<br />\n又少一個人上去消費"},{"pid":"a246359c775379ac5256f965a1dc623b546f5fa6","tid":1785826,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:35:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0d050673d0eecdc9b2d03bdb2bedf05be77a59d7","tid":1785826,"uid":72633,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:37:52.000Z","msg":"cls 其實好撚大鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢係連任區議員<br />\n唔係新當選<br />\n<br />\n咁其實分分鐘係所有非建制派嘅區議員都唔入得大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f54759d5c15a18335e9ba466445028aabe4dea8","tid":1785826,"uid":55453,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T17:40:08.000Z","msg":"返到黎，又冇屈你叫雞算好彩"},{"pid":"219786b9